  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to confirm the long-term efficacy (remission and
      maintenance in remission) of current validated treatments. Each patient will be followed
      during 3 years in this non-interventional trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
